---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
import ServiceExplore from '../../components/ServiceExplore.astro';
---

<Layout
  title="Tooth Extractions — Oasis Dental Care, Huntington Beach"
  description="Gentle tooth extractions in Huntington Beach. Precision removal with care and comfort. Dr. Jason Fu at Oasis Dental Care. Call (714) 893-2106."
  page="services"
>

<section class="phero">
  <div class="wrap">
    <div class="crumbs"><a href="/">Home</a><span class="sep">/</span><a href="/services">Services</a><span class="sep">/</span><span style="color:#cfe6e2">Extractions</span></div>
    <span class="tag">General dentistry</span>
    <h1>Extractions</h1>
    <p>Gentle, precise removal—focused on your comfort and recovery.</p>
    <div class="acts">
      <a class="btn" href="/contact">Schedule a consultation <svg class="ico" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M5 12h14M13 6l6 6-6 6"/></svg></a>
      <a class="btn btn-ghost" href="tel:7148932106">Call (714) 893-2106</a>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="pad">
  <div class="wrap">
    <div class="split">
      <div>

        <div class="img-ph reveal">
          <div class="img-ph-ic"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24"><rect x="3" y="3" width="18" height="18" rx="3"/><circle cx="8.5" cy="9" r="1.5"/><path d="m21 15-5-5L5 21"/></svg></div>
          <span class="img-ph-lbl">Photo placeholder</span>
          <span class="img-ph-desc">Reassuring clinical shot — clean, calm environment</span>
        </div>

        <div class="prose reveal">
          <span class="tag">Overview</span>
          <h2>When removal is the right choice, we make it easy.</h2>
          <p>Sometimes removing a tooth is the healthiest choice. Our extractions are performed with precision and care, always with an eye toward your comfort, smooth recovery, and next steps.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="prose reveal" style="margin-top:48px">
          <h3>When Is an Extraction Necessary?</h3>
          <ul>
            <li>Severe decay that can't be restored</li>
            <li>Advanced gum disease compromising the tooth</li>
            <li>Overcrowding before orthodontic treatment</li>
            <li>Broken tooth that can't be repaired</li>
            <li>Impacted wisdom teeth</li>
          </ul>

          <div class="img-ph reveal">
            <div class="img-ph-ic"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24"><rect x="3" y="3" width="18" height="18" rx="3"/><circle cx="8.5" cy="9" r="1.5"/><path d="m21 15-5-5L5 21"/></svg></div>
            <span class="img-ph-lbl">Photo placeholder</span>
            <span class="img-ph-desc">Calm patient consultation — nothing alarming</span>
          </div>

          <h3>What to Expect</h3>
          <ul>
            <li>Local anesthesia to fully numb the area</li>
            <li>Gentle, controlled removal</li>
            <li>Gauze and after-care instructions provided</li>
            <li>Follow-up if needed</li>
          </ul>

          <h3>After Your Extraction</h3>
          <p>Most patients recover within a few days. We'll give you detailed instructions on diet, activity, and caring for the site. If a replacement option (implant or bridge) makes sense for you, we'll discuss it at the same appointment.</p>

          <div class="img-ph reveal">
            <div class="img-ph-ic"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24"><rect x="3" y="3" width="18" height="18" rx="3"/><circle cx="8.5" cy="9" r="1.5"/><path d="m21 15-5-5L5 21"/></svg></div>
            <span class="img-ph-lbl">Photo placeholder</span>
            <span class="img-ph-desc">Patient receiving post-care instructions from team member</span>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="reveal" style="margin-top:48px">
          <span class="tag">Common questions</span>
          <h2 class="prose" style="margin-top:8px">Good to know.</h2>
          <div class="faq">
            <details open><summary>Will the extraction hurt?</summary><p>The area is fully numbed before treatment. You may feel pressure but not pain. Post-extraction soreness is normal and typically resolves within 2–3 days.</p></details>
            <details><summary>How long is the recovery?</summary><p>Most patients feel back to normal within 3–5 days. We'll give you specific guidelines based on your case.</p></details>
            <details><summary>What should I eat after an extraction?</summary><p>Stick to soft foods for the first day or two—yogurt, mashed potatoes, soup. Avoid hot liquids, straws, and smoking, which can disrupt healing.</p></details>
          </div>
        </div>

      </div>

      <aside>
        <div class="scard reveal">
          <div class="hd"><div class="grid-ov"></div><h3>Schedule an extraction consultation</h3><p>Most extractions completed in one visit</p></div>
          <div class="bd">
            <div class="row"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24"><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="9"/><path d="M12 7v5l3 2"/></svg><span>Most appointments 30–60 min</span></div>
            <div class="row"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M20 6 9 17l-5-5"/></svg><span>Most insurance accepted &amp; verified</span></div>
            <div class="row"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M12 2 4 5v6c0 5 3.5 9 8 11 4.5-2 8-6 8-11V5l-8-3z"/></svg><span>Gentle technique — comfort is our priority</span></div>
            <div class="divider"></div>
            <a class="btn" href="/contact">Schedule an Extraction Consultation</a>
            <a class="btn btn-out" href="tel:7148932106" style="justify-content:center">Call (714) 893-2106</a>
          </div>
        </div>
      </aside>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<ServiceExplore />

</Layout>
